## Useful Commands

(Update as the project grows. Cursor can run these for context.)

### Backend
```bash
# Run dev server
cd backend && uvicorn app.main:app --reload

# Run tests
cd backend && pytest

# Lint and format
cd backend && ruff check . && ruff format .

# Create a migration
cd backend && alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

# Run migrations
cd backend && alembic upgrade head
```

### Frontend
```bash
# Dev server
cd frontend && npm run dev

# Type check
cd frontend && npm run type-check

# Build
cd frontend && npm run build
```

### Infra
```bash
# Spin up everything (Postgres, Redis, Qdrant, Langfuse)
docker compose up -d

# Tear down
docker compose down

# View logs
docker compose logs -f [service-name]
```

