## Open Questions / Decisions Log

(Append decisions here as they're made. Helps future Cursor — and future you — understand why things are the way they are.)

- **[DATE]** — Picked Anthropic API over OpenAI for initial phases because of better streaming, larger context, and the developer wants Cursor experience.
- **[DATE]** — Picked Qdrant over Pinecone for self-hostability and learning value.
- **[DATE]** — Picked LangGraph over CrewAI/AutoGen because LangGraph is the most production-used agent framework in 2026 and has clearer state machine semantics.
- **[DATE]** — Picked Celery over Temporal initially for simplicity; will reconsider at Phase 8.

